{"tid":1347583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方稱暫時無情報顯示黑社會將出來襲擊市民","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T06:36:31.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f56449d74d6986af98af4dde381bb54eaccfbf1e","tid":1347583,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"多名民主派立法會議員和元朗區議員，聯同一批市民，走進元朗警署報案室抗議，不滿警方昨晚執法不力，令不少人昨晚在西鐵元朗站受襲，要求警方交代元朗今日是否安全。元朗區指揮官李偉文到場說，暫時警方接獲的情報中，沒有顯示黑社會份子會出來襲擊市民。<br />\n<br />\n李偉文表示，警方有策略調配資源，巡邏車和快速應變部隊仍在街上服務，盡力令市民日常生活不受影響，警方一接報一定全力以赴到場處理，亦會留意事態發展。李偉文說昨晚的情況由重案組調查，鎖定目標人物後會盡力拘捕，希望市民繼續支持警方。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員朱凱廸說，李偉文沒有保證元朗區的安全，擔心昨晚情況可能再發生，呼籲市民要互相幫助。"},{"pid":"db0ef79e7add314b421cd9d4db654552de5a5f92","tid":1347583,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190722/59849870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849870&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=6aab8a0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849870&h=6b48c595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190722/59849870</a>"},{"pid":"adf2c61e7bfda19af6b29b83c06b2776f258b3fc","tid":1347583,"uid":217844,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:23:52.000Z","msg":"屌收撚皮啦佢地噚廢柴黑警"},{"pid":"fc4bbc341eb3a982d7f91c2470d58463460faca5","tid":1347583,"uid":166616,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"可能便衣警黎呢 邊有黑社會"},{"pid":"aed6294a6330d1f33119d35a6595bce895013aba","tid":1347583,"uid":254371,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為香港最大黑社會就係