cgovern.house.gov/contact/zip-auth.htm</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repmcgovern\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepmcgovern&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=e10f04a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repmcgovern</a><br />\n<br />\n美國媒體清單<br />\n@washingtonpost<br />\n@BBCWorld<br />\n@CBSNews<br />\n@cnni<br />\n@FoxNews<br />\n<br />\n美國總統清單<br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n@VP<br />\n<br />\nTemplate:<br />\nDear Sir/Madam, I am writing as a Hong Kong citizen to inform you of the State Terrorism by the HK government in July 21. The police and triad gangs cooperated to assault citizens. <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6cXRFR8Uhl4&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=63b650eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4</a> We need humanitarian aid to protect residents and travelers. <br />\n請自行加減字數。光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"998f961b8767e4e935d8ee34a1d5ce6e9b96bdb9","tid":1347583,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"成報：中共煽動香港群眾內鬥， 救林鄭月娥<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1311160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1311160</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7980f6aeef7029a5b787d40951b19b5a97f7b26e","tid":1347583,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:31:14.000Z","msg":"警 黑一家親. <br />\n拎哂鐵通都話無武器, 有咩講唔出."},{"pid":"707abca3f79185cf9eac16d046dd51fea8aa6c30","tid":1347583,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:31:34.000Z","msg":"沒有顯示黑社會份子會出來襲擊市民。<br />\n<br />\n因為係黑社會打黑社會"},{"pid":"d82eebf96c88c2c9f577635b773ca8dfc898824c","tid":1347583,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"所有元朗人即刻走！走唔到留室內！流浮山有200刀手落